---
import GuideLayout from "../../layouts/GuideLayout.astro";
const title = "Post Construction Window Cleaning";
const description = "How windows should be cleaned safely after building or renovation work.";
---
<GuideLayout title={title} description={description}>
<p>Windows often collect plaster dust, paint splatter and adhesive residue during construction.</p>
<h2>Common residue</h2>
<p>Paint, silicone and dust frequently adhere to glass and frames after renovation.</p>
<h2>Cleaning approach</h2>
<p>Professional cleaning removes residue carefully without scratching glass or damaging frames.</p>
</GuideLayout>
